## 🎯 What You Can Build with Stitch

### Website Types
- 🏠 **Landing Pages** — Product launches, portfolios, agencies
- 📊 **Dashboards** — Analytics, SaaS admin panels, CRMs
- 🛍️ **E-Commerce** — Product pages, checkout flows
- 📱 **Mobile Apps** — iOS/Android style UIs
- 📰 **Content Sites** — Blogs, news, documentation

### Design Features
- **AI Text-to-UI** — Describe what you want, get a full design
- **Image-to-UI** — Upload a screenshot or sketch → editable UI
- **URL-to-UI** — Provide a website URL → extract and redesign it
- **Conversational Editing** — Refine designs by chatting
- **Multi-Screen Flows** — Generate complete app user journeys
- **Responsive Layouts** — Desktop, tablet, and mobile views

### Export Options
- **HTML + CSS** — Clean, production-ready code
- **React Components** — Modern component-based code
- **Figma Sync** — Export directly to Figma for team collaboration

