## 🎨 Design System Configuration

When creating a design system, you can customize:

| Property | Options |
|---|---|
| **Color Mode** | Light / Dark |
| **Primary Color** | Any hex color (e.g., `#6366F1`) |
| **Font Family** | Inter, Roboto, Manrope, Outfit, etc. |
| **Corner Roundness** | Sharp → Pill-shaped |
| **Color Palette** | Vibrant, Fidelity, Expressive, etc. |
| **Design Instructions** | Free-form markdown instructions |

