## 💡 Pro Tips

> [!TIP]
> **Be specific in your prompts!** Instead of "make a website", say "Create a dark-mode SaaS landing page for a project management tool with a purple gradient hero, feature cards, pricing table with 3 tiers, and a CTA footer."

> [!NOTE]
> **Multiple Websites**: You can create unlimited projects in Stitch. Each project is independent with its own screens and design system.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Export to Code**: Once you're happy with a design, I can help you export it as actual HTML/CSS/React code and save it to your local project folder (`c:\Users\Amit Kumar\Desktop\FP`).

---

## 🗺️ Getting Started — Choose Your Path

1. **Create a brand new website** → Tell me the type of site and style
2. **Continue your existing project** → I can show you its current screens
3. **Create a new design system** → Set up your brand colors & fonts first
4. **Generate variants** → Get multiple design options to choose from

**What would you like to design first?**
